sentences: He initially used the stage name Aparatec, releasing an EP of material under that name in 2007.
His first release as Rival Consoles was issued later in 2007 by Erased Tapes Records, which has released all of his albums and EPs.
His track "Recovery" was used in a 2020 television commercial for Blue Dragon foods.
Vemeer EP (2007, Erased Tapes, as Aparatec)
